net.sf.jclec.mo.evaluation.fitness

Interface INSGA2MOFitness

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ICrowdingDistanceMOFitness
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    IGrEAMOFitness
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GrEAMOFitness, NSGA2MOFitness, NSGA3MOFitness

    public interface INSGA2MOFitness
extends ICrowdingDistanceMOFitness
    This interface defines the methods that the fitness of a solution should provide in order to use some of the procedures defined by NSGA-II algorithm.

    HISTORY:

    • (AR|JRR|SV, 1.0, March 2018) First release.

    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Aurora Ramirez (AR), Jose Raul Romero (JRR), Sebastian Ventura (SV)

    Knowledge Discovery and Intelligent Systems (KDIS) Research Group: http://www.uco.es/grupos/kdis

    See Also:
    NSGA2
